{"tid":1783144,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"肥婆奶奶與妹仔 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-12-14T14:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T14:42:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f5449c30d907fcc90ad4cf10059c5d0d2f7e5f44","tid":1783144,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:19:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191214/20824671/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191214%2F20824671%2F&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWvG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=64f835fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191214%2F20824671%2F&h=353cfa87\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191214/20824671/</a><br />\n<br />\n肥婆奶奶與妹仔 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191214/large/1576227487_a36a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191214%2Flarge%2F1576227487_a36a.jpg&h=1410f7f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真難得，妹仔上位至今，沒做過一件對的事，沒講過一句對的話，所有決策都是錯，都是禍&hellip;&hellip;要有多大能耐，才可達此境界？以前劣跡斑斑不說了，只這一兩天，保皇黨區選慘敗，林鄭的「解穢酒」、「公帑重金回收落選垃圾兼道歉（人家不領情不接受）」、「罵港人去外國唱衰香港」、「國際專家小組成員批林鄭盲撐之監警會無權調查集體退出」&hellip;&hellip;全都是一巴一巴的打臉，不過妹仔已是無血性無人性之行屍走肉了，哪有表情？<br />\n<br />\n反而其好姊妹僭建驊有點看頭。損友M是粵語陳片迷（我也是），她說肥驊就似肥婆奶奶譚蘭卿，惡死能登又霸道，常遭縮骨新馬仔撚化，被鄧碧雲的巴辣好姐整治，灰頭土臉兼語塞，一如被送中照肺後之沮喪。不過譚蘭卿（1908~1981）是女丑生，在簡單純真善惡分明的社會，惡得來都很可愛。<br />\n<br />\n當肥婆奶奶是好命，生活富泰養尊處優，才可如此豐腴飽滿。但肥驊不是惡，是兇──鷹鼻反眼手指指，繼續助黑警濫捕濫檢控，沒有退路（不知在京時有否被植入晶片？）。且這回佈局藉「甩骹骨折」謀辭職不果，為了連戲，未來一年都得與「吊帶」相依相伴，否則自揭謊言。着草失敗，道具論盡，還酷愛樽領衫露餡，這回再兇也有點低智。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"f0a286816eb3efa56a46f78725b35a22785bb28c","tid":1783144,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:20:25.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"66fec017f5e12f2c345a5dbec95defa03ced8afd","tid":1783144,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FDHdKiw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFDHdKiw.jpg&h=779c8437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VCCpQSW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVCCpQSW.jpg&h=7105947f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1e7010e2a90efd459a535aeaba1e84ebdd1dc20","tid":1783144,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:42:16.000Z","msg":"睇過胭脂扣 霸王別姬就知李碧華幾憎共產黨 佢係未回歸前已經知道香港未來唔樂觀<br />\n思想走幾前既人<br />\n而家先知佢有寫專欄"}]}